                impact: "City-level climate action plans prepared in 6 cities. Guidance document for comprehensive disaster management plan in Kochi. 4 regional plans as part of NITI Aayog\u2019s Growth Hubs project. State-level heat mitigation strategy in Tamil Nadu.",
                whatsNeeded: "Citizen volunteers and local leaders. Community meeting spaces. Local organisations or CBOs for citizen mobilisation. Access to publicly available data sets and maps.",
