                whatIsIt: "An institutional neighbourhood development project initiated by Gandhinagar Urban Development Authority (GUDA) in the Knowledge Hub precinct (TP Scheme 19, Raysan). It involves the redesign of 6.5 km of roads under a Complete Street framework, with development of utilities, streetscapes, and landscaping to create safe and accessible NMT-friendly streets around a cluster of educational institutes and improve their connectivity to the upcoming metro station. Key collaborators include Multimedia Consultants Pvt Ltd, JIT Engineering Services Pvt Ltd, GUDA, and Knowledge Hub Consortium institutions.",
